<blockquote>
  <p>This is a course project in the course <em>Introduction to Information System and Programming</em> in ISTD major, SUTD. The course is about Java Programming, Android Develop and Object Oriented Programming. The final project of the course is designing and building an Android App related to IoT and AI. We, a group of 3, developed an App aiming at solving the class attendance problem with face detection, as well as the class participation problem. Generally speaking, I designed the major functions and interaction of the App, the visual interface, the poster and was fully in charge of the front-end developing and 2 of 4 app functions developing. The projects has been selected to the ISTD major show next year as an excellent work.<br />
